dialogue: I'm just sayin', if I see one more picture of Ed Begley, Jr. in that stupid electric car, I'm gonna shoot myself! I mean, don't get me wrong... I'm not against environmental issues per se.... it's just that guy!
I mean, come on, buddy, get a real car!
Exactly! And you just know I'm gonna be the guy caught behind this hammerhead in traffic!
Well, I’m not gonna talk because…
